{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_51_02",
  "title": "佐伯遙子",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_mountain-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり引き返した方がいいんじゃないかしら\n本当に人が通っていい道なの？",
      "startTime": 4.6000000755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.1000000755
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "熟練のキャンパーさんに教えてもらったから大丈夫よ\nソロキャンプ歴一年の私に任せて！",
      "startTime": 11.2000000755,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8023.518605500001,
          "startTime": 19.223518681
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.4000002026
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "一年って……命を預けるには不安な年数だわ",
      "startTime": 14.4000002026,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.8000002026
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "きゃーーっ！！　今、なんか背中に落ちた！\nむ、むむむ虫！？",
      "startTime": 23.1666668693,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.4666668693
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　この時期、虫はほとんどいないと\n思ったんだけど……",
      "startTime": 28.3000002026,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.0000002026
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "大きめの葉よ。こんなことでいちいち騒がないで\nそれより、莉央、貴方の頭の上に――",
      "startTime": 34.1333335359,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.9666668693
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "嘘！？　何！？　なんなの！？\nやだ、早く取って！",
      "startTime": 39.4000002026,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6666.670481400004,
          "startTime": 46.066670684
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_heart-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6666.670481400004,
          "startTime": 46.066670684
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.1333335359
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "本当にうるさいわね。たかが虫じゃない\nちょっと止まりなさい",
      "startTime": 44.6000002026,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.7666729728
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "あ痛っ！　いきなり何すんのよ！",
      "startTime": 46.7666729728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.5333396394
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "貴方が払って、って言うから払ったのよ\n感謝しなさい",
      "startTime": 52.2000063061,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "取ってくれたのはありがたいんですが\n頭を叩いていいとは言ってません！",
      "startTime": 55.7333426912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.6333426912
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "……虫ごときでギャーギャーと\n貴方それでもリズノワのリーダーなの？",
      "startTime": 61.5333426912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.3666760246
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "まあまあ、誰にだって苦手なものはあるわ。でも\nmihoさんてば凄いのね。全然動揺しないんだもの",
      "startTime": 69.5000093579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.3333426912
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……それより、キャンプ場にはあとどれくらいで\n着くのよ。近道なんでしょう",
      "startTime": 78.7666760246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_jungle-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.4000093579
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、そろそろだと思うわ\nもうひと踏ん張り、頑張りましょうね！",
      "startTime": 83.8666760246,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4066.661632100008,
          "startTime": 87.9333376567
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 87.4000093579
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 87.4000093579
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "やっと着いたわ……\nもう日が暮れちゃったじゃない",
      "startTime": 91.9333554069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "正規ルートを歩いてたら、到着は深夜だったのかしら",
      "startTime": 94.3666887402,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 98.7000220735
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "その可能性は高かったかも……\nとにかく、無事に着いて良かったわ！",
      "startTime": 102.0333554069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "スタッフさんは到着にもうちょっとかかるみたい\n先にタープの設営をしましょうか！",
      "startTime": 108.6333554069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 111.4000220735
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "なんでそんなに元気なのよ。こっちは慣れない山道を\n歩いたんだから……少し休憩させてちょうだい",
      "startTime": 115.3668489575,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 119.3333554069
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうよね。……つい浮かれちゃったわ\n東屋で休んだら、キャンプスタートよ～！",
      "startTime": 124.9666887402,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 129.4000220735
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "スタッフさんが間に合ったのはいいけど、インタビュー\nされながらテントを組み立てるのって、結構大変なのね",
      "startTime": 133.5333630363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 138.0666963696
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんの手際の良さ、なかなかだったわ。あんなに\nかっこ良くペグを打ち付けるアイドルいないわよ！",
      "startTime": 142.1333630363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 145.5000297029
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ありがとう。遙子の的確な指示のおかげだわ\nmihoさんの方はどうですか？　火は起こせました？",
      "startTime": 150.1333630363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 153.6333630363
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、問題ないわ\n遙子に下準備を頼んだアヒージョも煮えてきたところよ",
      "startTime": 155.9666963696,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3599.9702971000147,
          "startTime": 159.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_camp-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "camp-00-night",
      "startTime": 159.4000043233
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_51_02-hrk009.m4a",
